        yang luar biasa dengan solusi aplikasi dari Devghuraba Teknologi.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-12">
        <a
          href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Ghuraba+Developer"
          target="_blank"
          class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded px-8 h-10.5 bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          Coba Gratis Sekarang
          <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="ml-2 h-5 w-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
        </a>

        <a
          href={`https://wa.me/6289699250746?text=${message}`}
          target="_blank"
          class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded px-8 h-10.5 bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          <Icon name="tabler:message" class="mr-2 h-5 w-5" />
